_sText:
This is my first little map, a Bomb/Defuse map taking place in an enclosed valley. I am aware that you are able to sniper from across the map, I plan on fixing that later.

There is also a secret room I call, The Crib. There is nothing in it but a teleporter exit that takes you onto the rocks, and some Pokemon.

I would love feedback on the map about what you think about it, and what you think I should change. Have fun!
